    Class
    Description
    ActivitySchedulerApplication
    Main application class for the Activity Scheduler application.

    MembershipController
    REST controller for managing Membership entities.
    MembershipController.MembershipRequest
    Request DTO for creating a membership.
    MembershipController.StatusUpdateRequest
    Request DTO for updating membership status.
    MembershipId
    Composite primary key for Membership entity.

    Repository interface for Membership entity operations.
    MembershipService
    Service class for managing Membership entities.
    MembershipStatus
    Enum representing the possible status values for a membership.

    OrganizationCreationRequest

    OrganizationRepository
    Repository interface for Organization entity operations.
    OrganizationService
    Service class for managing Organization entities.
    User
    User entity representing a user in the activity scheduler system.
    UserController
    REST controller for managing User entities.
    UserRegistrationRequest
    DTO for user registration requests.
    UserRepository
    Repository interface for User entity operations.
